      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s specimen featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through its individual throttle bodies. Mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, the drivetrain utilizes a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis has been enhanced with preventative subframe reinforcement and fresh bushings to maintain torsional rigidity. Recent comprehensive maintenance includes a VANOS system overhaul and a shim-and-bucket valve adjustment to ensure the high-revving valvetrain meets factory specifications. While the exterior shows minor signs of spirited road use, the mechanical components are dialed in for a visceral, analog performance experience.",
